xed (no strace wrapping).\n      expect(mockSpawn).toHaveBeenLastCalledWith(\n        \"bash\",\n        [\"-c\", \"cat /secret.txt\"],\n        expect.objectContaining({ cwd: \"/test/cwd\" }),",
